Title: Computes and Plots Consonance (Confidence) Intervals, P-Values,
        and S-Values to Form Consonance and Surprisal Functions
Version: 2.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Zad R.", "Chow", , "zad@lesslikely.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
